** sym_path: /foss/pdks/ciel/sky130/versions/8afc8346a57fe1ab7934ba5a6056ea8b43078e71/sky130A/libs.tech/xschem/sky130_tests/test_sweep_mos_w.sym
** sch_path: /foss/pdks/ciel/sky130/versions/8afc8346a57fe1ab7934ba5a6056ea8b43078e71/sky130A/libs.tech/xschem/sky130_tests/test_sweep_mos_w.sch
.subckt test_sweep_mos_w
V1 G GND 1
